snippet.title: Delco Press Club - The State of Broadcasting: From Academics to the Workplace
snippet.description: Neumann Media's Director, Sean McDonald, joins the Delco Press Club to talk about the state of broadcasting during COVID, the changes made in the academic and professional realm, and what advances have come because of the pandemic. Thanks to Lisa Roberts Cadorette for moderating, and Vincent Cotter, Amanda Cunningham, and Patrick McMullin for producing.
